  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223198/RenderMan_Dirt_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601472&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223198/RenderMan_Dirt_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601472&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223276\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Dirt_1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223198\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e423ad5e-9de7-4f0e-a939-5a41239971d9\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/><em>PxrDirt</em> renders local geometric occlusion. This is useful for applying shading effects to nooks and crevices.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"9dc6ab69-965b-4a8c-8d19-6cbf416362b4\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>A traditional ambient occlusion effect can be accomplished by setting the occluded color to black and unoccluded color to white.</p></div></div><h3 id=\"PxrDirt-Parameters\">Parameters</h3><h4 id=\"PxrDirt-OccludedandUnoccluded\">Occluded and Unoccluded</h4><p>Resulting colors for occluded and unoccluded shading.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrDirt_dirtColor0.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_dirtColor0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223198/PxrDirt_dirtColor0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223270\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrDirt_dirtColor0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223198\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"6c9b9533-ae2c-4402-8fba-8aa098137626\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_dirtColor0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_dirtColor0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrDirt_dirtColor1.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_dirtColor1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223198/PxrDirt_dirtColor1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223267\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrDirt_dirtColor1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223198\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"334be742-b232-44a1-a1bd-f3f80dddd929\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_dirtColor1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_dirtColor1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrDirt_dirtColor2.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_dirtColor2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223198/PxrDirt_dirtColor2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223264\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrDirt_dirtColor2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223198\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"fc72c9aa-2972-4d01-8aca-7c17bce72fc5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_dirtColor2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_dirtColor2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h4 id=\"PxrDirt-NumSamples\">Num Samples</h4><p>Controls the number of occlusion samples per camera hit point. More samples reduces can the noise at the cost of increased render time.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"PxrDirt_numSamples0.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_numSamples0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601068&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223198/PxrDirt_numSamples0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601068&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223258\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrDirt_numSamples0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223198\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"901debf6-7557-4ebd-a566-4c24eb1a52b5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_numSamples0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601068&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_numSamples0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601068&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"PxrDirt_numSamples1.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_numSamples1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601068&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223198/PxrDirt_numSamples1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601068&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223261\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrDirt_numSamples1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223198\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"6ead0231-5865-4dec-a928-98952d05f5c8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_numSamples1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601068&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_numSamples1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601068&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h4 id=\"PxrDirt-SampleDistribution\">Sample Distribution</h4><p>Possible values are <em>uniform</em> and <em>cosine</em> (Lambertian).</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"PxrDirt_distribution0.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_distribution0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330600882&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223198/PxrDirt_distribution0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330600882&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223252\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrDirt_distribution0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223198\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"585ad6ad-174f-4704-af90-894f21cc4eb7\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_distribution0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330600882&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_distribution0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330600882&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"PxrDirt_distribution1.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_distribution1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601068&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223198/PxrDirt_distribution1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601068&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223255\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrDirt_distribution1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223198\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"decee034-d419-49b5-81d5-c35923ad5a7e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_distribution1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601068&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_distribution1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330601068&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-layout=\"default\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p><br/></p></th><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p><strong>Description</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p><strong>Uniform</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Rays are not weighted in any particular direction in the hemisphere above the shading point.</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p><strong>Cosine</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Cosine distribution is commonly used to render ambient occlusion.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h4 id=\"PxrDirt-CosineSpread\">Cosine Spread</h4><p>Sample spread of rays when using <em>cosine</em> distribution. A value of 1.0 gives a perfect Lambertian distribution.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrDirt_cosineSpread0.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_cosineSpread0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330600881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223198/PxrDirt_cosineSpread0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330600881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223246\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrDirt_cosineSpread0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223198\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"62f99548-3b98-4194-bc77-17165d119388\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_cosineSpread0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330600881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_cosineSpread0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330600881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrDirt_cosineSpread1.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_cosineSpread1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330600881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223198/PxrDirt_cosineSpread1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330600881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223249\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrDirt_cosineSpread1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223198\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"442542b4-99d4-49fe-8213-361d59a4c7f3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_cosineSpread1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330600881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_cosineSpread1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330600881&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrDirt_cosineSpread2.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542223198/PxrDirt_cosineSpread2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330600696&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542223198/PxrDirt_cosineSpread2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330600696&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542223243\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrDirt_cosineSpread2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542223198\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ec676f4c-5734-42f3-83e2-a051e64215fd\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/downlo